OL,5, The UK's energy regulator has announced
OL,6, plans to better protect customers who  
OL,7, pay their bills through direct debit.  
OL,9,FOfgem accused some firms of using      
OL,10,Fcustomers' accumulated credit like an  
OL,11,F"interest-free company credit card".   
OL,13,FProposals include tightening the rules 
OL,14,Fon the level of direct debits that     
OL,15,Fsuppliers can charge to "ensure credit 
OL,16,Fbalances do not become excessive".     
OL,18,FOfgem also wants to protect credit     
OL,19,Fbalances when suppliers fail so the    
OL,20,Fcosts are not picked up by customers.  
